There's no need for that.

1566
02:22:41.637 --> 02:22:42.680 line:82%
Why not?

1567
02:22:42.763 --> 02:22:44.390 line:82%
He has just returned after seven years.

1568
02:22:44.473 --> 02:22:46.058 line:82%
