for another seven.

1569
02:22:46.141 --> 02:22:48.435 line:82%
You are trying to guard a soldier is it?

1570
02:22:48.519 --> 02:22:50.938 line:82%
Rehan, do you want me to radio them?

1571
02:22:51.522 --> 02:22:53.274 line:82%
No, I will have to do it myself.

1572
02:22:55.067 --> 02:22:57.194 line:82%
Let him give his status report

1573
02:22:57.278 --> 02:23:01.573 line:82%
then you can keep him
imprisoned here forever, right Rehan?

1574
02:23:01.657 --> 02:23:04.743 line:82%
Fine, now no more discussion.
What do they say in Punjabi?

1575
