02:25:04.613 --> 02:25:05.656 line:82%
Grandpa!

1596
02:25:08.367 --> 02:25:09.368 line:82%
Come on, Rehan.

1597
02:25:10.702 --> 02:25:13.580 line:82%
Let's go to the Colonel's house
