They are fighting for their independence.

1607
02:26:03.297 --> 02:26:05.549 line:82%
And who will run this country of theirs?

1608
02:26:05.632 --> 02:26:07.468 line:82%
-The IKF?
-No.

1609
02:26:08.802 --> 02:26:11.221 line:82%
Whoever the people of Kashmir elect
in fair elections.

1610
02:26:12.389 --> 02:26:16.727 line:82%
