1613
02:26:48.634 --> 02:26:53.430 line:82%
I was doubtful when I saw the news,
but by then, it was too late.

1614
02:26:55.474 --> 02:26:58.352 line:82%
I had my doubts.

1615
02:26:59.520 --> 02:27:03.440 line:82%
Today, I was certain when
I found this trigger in your pocket.

1616
02:27:05.984 --> 02:27:07.986 line:82%
You can't do anything now.

1617
02:27:08.654 --> 02:27:10.864 line:82%
I am going to radio the military
and hand you over.

1618
02:27:11.949 --> 02:27:13.033 line:82%
Colonel!

1619
02:27:13.992 --> 02:27:15.369 line:82%
Come outside.

1620
02:27:16.745 --> 02:27:18.997 line:82%
-Please sir, give me that trigger.
-No.

1621
02:27:19.081 --> 02:27:21.041 line:82%
All this will be over in a couple of days.

1622
02:27:21.124 --> 02:27:23.210 line:82%
Then, I can stay
with Zooni and Rehan forever.

1623
02:27:23.293 --> 02:27:26.338 line:82%
I would rather wish they be dead.
I will never give you this. Never.

1624
02:27:36.890 --> 02:27:38.225 line:82%
No!

1625
02:27:38.308 --> 02:27:40.644 line:82%
Don't you dare, Rehan!

1626
02:27:42.229 --> 02:27:43.647 line:82%
No!

1627
02:27:51.655 --> 02:27:53.490 line:82%
No!

1628
02:28:02.040 --> 02:28:04.543 line:82%
Shalimar 1, target is coming.

