1631
02:28:16.888 --> 02:28:18.432 line:82%
My son, Rehan!

1632
02:28:19.349 --> 02:28:22.227 line:82%
God be praised a million times.

1633
02:28:22.311 --> 02:28:23.520 line:82%
You're alive!

1634
02:28:24.605 --> 02:28:26.857 line:82%
Do you have what I want?

1635
02:28:28.233 --> 02:28:29.818 line:82%
Yes, I have it with me.

1636
02:28:30.277 --> 02:28:31.361 line:82%
What's the matter?

1637
02:28:31.737 --> 02:28:34.031 line:82%
I'm tired that's all.

1638
02:28:35.157 --> 02:28:36.533 line:82%
I just want all this to end.

1639
02:28:36.617 --> 02:28:37.618 line:82%
Look here...

1640
02:28:37.701 --> 02:28:39.077 line:82%
I know what I have to do.

1641
02:28:40.037 --> 02:28:41.788 line:82%
Come here and take what it is you want.

1642
02:28:43.457 --> 02:28:49.463 line:82%
The coordinates here are loc rep 34,74.

1643
02:28:50.464 --> 02:28:52.924 line:82%
Mount 2,730, 500 house.

1644
02:28:54.968 --> 02:28:56.178 line:82%
That was him.

1645
02:28:57.262 --> 02:28:59.431 line:82%
Thank God he hasn't reached
his people yet.

1646
02:28:59.514 --> 02:29:02.434 line:82%
There is very heavy fog right now.

1647
02:29:03.185 --> 02:29:07.898 line:82%
We will try and be there tomorrow morning.
God be with you.

1648
02:29:19.368 --> 02:29:21.828 line:82%
Sorry, ma'am,
he gave his location in code.

1649
02:29:21.912 --> 02:29:23.747 line:82%
We will need some time to break it.

1650
02:29:26.249 --> 02:29:27.959 line:82%
Give Ranade the code to break.

1651
02:29:28.043 --> 02:29:29.503 line:82%
-Keep the ground search going.
-Yes, sir.

1652
02:29:29.586 --> 02:29:33.090 line:82%
And continue monitoring
the frequency he called from.

1653
02:29:33.548 --> 02:29:37.219 line:82%
We only have until tomorrow morning.
Contact the base camp.

1654
02:29:37.302 --> 02:29:40.138 line:82%
Are they ready with the sketch
of the imposter of Captain Ranjeev?

