1669
02:31:22.532 --> 02:31:25.452 line:82%
He went missing eight days ago.

1670
02:31:25.702 --> 02:31:27.788 line:82%
He is also carrying an electronic part.

1671
02:31:28.038 --> 02:31:30.624 line:82%
This is a sketch of himprovided by the army.

1672
02:31:30.749 --> 02:31:34.586 line:82%
If you see this man anywhere,please don't try and catch him yourself.

1673
02:31:34.669 --> 02:31:36.004 line:82%
He is armed and dangerous.

1674
02:31:36.087 --> 02:31:38.799 line:82%
Please contact your nearest policestation immediately.

1675
02:31:38.882 --> 02:31:40.884 line:82%
