from the same frequency.

1679
02:34:11.076 --> 02:34:13.119 line:82%
-Hello, can someone hear me?
-Hello!

1680
02:34:13.203 --> 02:34:14.704 line:82%
Hello, yes, we can hear you.

1681
02:34:14.788 --> 02:34:18.333 line:82%
I am Malini Tyagi
from the Anti-Terrorist Special Force.

1682
02:34:18.416 --> 02:34:19.584 line:82%
Who is this?

1683
02:34:20.335 --> 02:34:23.213 line:82%
I am Zooni Ali Beg speaking.

1684
02:34:24.422 --> 02:34:28.218 line:82%
My husband, I thought he was dead.

1685
02:34:28.677 --> 02:34:31.221 line:82%
But he came back nine days ago.

1686
02:34:31.972 --> 02:34:34.641 line:82%
I think he's the one you are looking for.

1687
02:34:36.768 --> 02:34:41.731 line:82%
