and my uncle, or maybe not.

1688
02:34:42.649 --> 02:34:45.819 line:82%
I don't know. I don't know anything.

1689
02:34:46.319 --> 02:34:48.446 line:82%
Just please help us.

1690
02:34:48.530 --> 02:34:50.281 line:82%
I am alone. It's just me and my son.

1691
02:34:52.575 --> 02:34:54.160 line:82%
And listen to me carefully.

1692
02:34:54.995 --> 02:34:58.123 line:82%
Does your husband have some sort of
an electronic part?

1693
02:34:58.331 --> 02:35:02.168 line:82%
Yes, hello!

1694
02:35:02.252 --> 02:35:04.629 line:82%
I saw it on TV.

1695
02:35:05.672 --> 02:35:07.048 line:82%
And now it's with me.

1696
02:35:09.259 --> 02:35:10.260 line:82%
It's him.

1697
02:35:10.343 --> 02:35:12.679 line:82%
Your husband is the onewe are looking for.

1698
02:35:13.179 --> 02:35:14.389 line:82%
He is the terrorist.

1699
02:35:20.020 --> 02:35:21.438 line:82%
Listen to me carefully, Zooni.

1700
02:35:21.521 --> 02:35:26.317 line:82%
I am going to tell you the most
important thing you will ever hear.

1701
02:35:26.401 --> 02:35:29.863 line:82%
If he leaves with that trigger,
if he joins his comrades they will use

1702
02:35:30.196 --> 02:35:34.534 line:82%
a nuclear bomb over our country.

1703
02:35:35.201 --> 02:35:37.412 line:82%
Millions of Indians will die.

1704
02:35:38.413 --> 02:35:43.918 line:82%
One of them can be my daughter.
Another can be your son.

1705
02:35:45.378 --> 02:35:46.838 line:82%
There will be complete destruction.

1706
02:35:46.963 --> 02:35:52.302 line:82%
And the only one who can stop it,
Zooni, is you!

1707
02:35:54.471 --> 02:35:58.516 line:82%
But, he is my husband.

1708
02:35:58.808 --> 02:36:01.144 line:82%
Tell me you will help us, Zooni.

1709
02:36:02.562 --> 02:36:07.192 line:82%
Tell me you will stop him,
whatever it takes.

1710
02:36:09.903 --> 02:36:12.781 line:82%
Yes.

1711
02:36:12.906 --> 02:36:15.825 line:82%
We have your location now, Zooni.

1712
