From me?

1719
02:37:23.476 --> 02:37:24.853 line:82%
From your Rehan?

1720
02:37:26.354 --> 02:37:27.981 line:82%
I have only one Rehan.

1721
02:37:29.232 --> 02:37:30.233 line:82%
My son.

1722
02:37:33.570 --> 02:37:35.655 line:82%
Dad, what happened?

1723
02:37:37.991 --> 02:37:40.577 line:82%
Nothing, son. Everything is fine.

1724
02:37:42.537 --> 02:37:43.621 line:82%
Go to sleep.

1725
02:37:46.749 --> 02:37:50.712 line:82%
What's the point?
You will kill him as well.

1726
02:37:52.589 --> 02:37:54.215 line:82%
I would rather die first.

1727
02:37:54.966 --> 02:37:57.093 line:82%
You killed Dad quite easily.

1728
02:38:02.015 --> 02:38:03.725 line:82%
I didn't kill him.

1729
02:38:05.685 --> 02:38:07.187 line:82%
It was an accident.

1730
02:38:10.940 --> 02:38:12.442 line:82%
And Colonel?

1731
02:38:23.536 --> 02:38:25.330 line:82%
Give me the trigger, Zooni.

1732
02:38:26.414 --> 02:38:28.124 line:82%
-No.
-Zooni!

1733
02:38:32.170 --> 02:38:33.504 line:82%
Give me that trigger.

1734
02:38:35.673 --> 02:38:40.345 line:82%
What will you do?
Kill me as well? Kill me.

1735
02:38:40.970 --> 02:38:45.350 line:82%
I've already died once because of you.
Why not once again?

1736
02:38:47.769 --> 02:38:51.314 line:82%
Zooni, despite all my lies,

1737
02:38:52.649 --> 02:38:54.776 line:82%
despite all the pain I have given you,

1738
02:38:56.236 --> 02:39:01.324 line:82%
do you believe that I love you?

1739
02:39:04.953 --> 02:39:06.496 line:82%
Then for the sake of that love,

1740
02:39:07.372 --> 02:39:09.040 line:82%
