his family with his own hands.

1747
02:39:37.318 --> 02:39:38.820 line:82%
I don't care about myself, Zooni.

1748
02:39:39.904 --> 02:39:42.740 line:82%
But I am not willing
to sacrifice Rehan or you.

1749
02:39:46.119 --> 02:39:50.748 line:82%
This is the only way...

1750
02:39:51.791 --> 02:39:56.963 line:82%
we will be able to live our lives
in peace again.

1751
02:40:00.800 --> 02:40:04.220 line:82%
And what about the lives of those
millions that will die from the bomb?

1752
02:40:04.554 --> 02:40:08.725 line:82%
No one will use the bomb.
It's just a threat.

1753
02:40:08.808 --> 02:40:12.353 line:82%
The governments of India and Pakistan
will have no other choice, but to give in.

1754
02:40:18.526 --> 02:40:23.573 line:82%
After all your lies,
how can I believe you now?

1755
02:40:28.536 --> 02:40:29.787 line:82%
Grandfather.

1756
02:40:31.956 --> 02:40:36.127 line:82%
Or the Indian Army whom I called.

1757
02:40:46.721 --> 02:40:47.764 line:82%
No.

1758
02:40:48.181 --> 02:40:49.349 line:82%
Grandfather.

1759
02:40:53.394 --> 02:40:54.437 line:82%
You can't leave.

1760
02:41:02.070 --> 02:41:05.365 line:82%
Take care of Rehan and yourself.

1761
02:41:07.158 --> 02:41:08.868 line:82%
I will be back tomorrow.

1762
02:41:32.100 --> 02:41:35.228 line:82%
Rehan! Please, for our son's sake.

1763
02:43:24.879 --> 02:43:27.215 line:82%
Rehan!

1764
02:43:35.056 --> 02:43:37.058 line:82%
Why, Rehan? Why?

1765
02:43:43.189 --> 02:43:47.610 line:82%
Rehan loves you more than you love Rehan.

1766
02:43:47.693 --> 02:43:49.028 line:82%
Don't say that.

1767
02:43:50.947 --> 02:43:52.198 line:82%
Please don't.

1768
02:44:02.375 --> 02:44:04.168 line:82%
Now I'm not scared.

1769
02:44:18.266 --> 02:44:19.350 line:82%
Rehan.

1770
02:44:24.730 --> 02:44:26.274 line:82%
Rehan!

1771
02:44:35.074 --> 02:44:39.662 line:82%
When I have your hands in mine

