1778
02:45:10.610 --> 02:45:12.987 line:82%
But to choose the better of two goods,

1779
02:45:13.446 --> 02:45:15.740 line:82%
or the lesser of two evils,

1780
02:45:17.575 --> 02:45:19.660 line:82%
these choices decide our lives.

1781
02:45:27.168 --> 02:45:29.211 line:82%
Rehan loves you a lot.

1782
02:45:33.215 --> 02:45:35.551 line:82%
And Zooni loves Rehan a lot.

